title: No slim model about Multilingual RecognitionAdd Android OCR Demo
body:
Thanks for your great android demo project.
It works quite well about images written in Chinese, and English. However it is not recognizing other languages, like Japanese, Korean, Russian because current model is not providing the languages except English and Korean.
I've seen there are multilingual recognition models, but all of them contain inference or trained model and do not support slim model.

Could you share any other slim model files(.nb) to recognize other language texts?

title: update face detect model
body:
### 更新人脸关键点检测 DEMO
-  使用 [PaddleHub](https://github.com/PaddlePaddle/PaddleHub/tree/release/v2.1/modules/image/face_detection) 推荐的 [超轻量人脸检测模型](https://www.paddlepaddle.org.cn/hubdetail?name=ultra_light_fast_generic_face_detector_1mb_640&en_category=FaceDetection)
    - 修改后处理函数：补充 `HardNms`函数
    - 效果：
       - 模型体积缩小( 3.1M ---> 1.7M)
       - 推理速度 (302ms ---> 58ms) 输入shape [1,3,640,480]
- 人脸关键点 DEMO： 只描出关键点、不描出人脸框

### 说明
- `REPO`中原来使用的模型 是 PaddleHub上一般 [人脸检测模型](https://github.com/PaddlePaddle/PaddleHub/tree/release/v2.1/modules/image/face_detection/pyramidbox_lite_mobile)

新增图片分类批量处理功能
body:
在原有图片分类只提供单张图片预测的功能的基础上，提供了批量图片预测的功能，开发者只需修改image_path即可实现功能的切换。
![image-20220718142407938](https://s2.loli.net/2022/07/18/l1DpfPXYiyGe2Kj.png)

并且采用了最新的PPLCNet图片分类模型，相比之前的mobilenet_v1模型，在树莓派4B/32G上的实际预测速度提高了整整64.7%
![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/65645246/179496824-686682be-a4af-46e1-8353-537fa45cd26a.png)
![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/65645246/179499399-6323d40c-b9e1-4f29-bc92-03f7ca42337f.png)
